    <div class="container my-4 py-4">
        <h5 class="card-title fs-2 fw-bolder">Most linux commands that you should know <hr class="w-75" /></h5>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">ls - list the files and directories in the current directory</span>
            <span id="myText" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">ls</span>
            <button id="cpy" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">cd - change the current directory</span>
            <span id="myText1" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">cd dir_name</span>
            <button id="cpy1" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent1()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">mkdir - create a new directory</span>
            <span id="myText2" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">mkdir mohit</span>
            <button id="cpy2" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent2()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">rmdir - remove a directory</span>
            <span id="myText3" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">rmdir mohit</span>
            <button id="cpy3" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent3()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">pwd - print the current working directory</span>
            <span id="myText4" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">pwd</span>
            <button id="cpy4" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent4()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">cp - copy files or directories</span>
            <span id="myText5" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">#We will copy a file called example.txt from the current directory to a directory called backup <br/> cp example.txt backup/</span>
            <button id="cpy5" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent5()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">mv - move or rename files or directories</span>
            <span id="myText6" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">mv example.txt backup/</span>
            <button id="cpy6" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent6()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">rm - remove files or directories</span>
            <span id="myText7" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">rm example.txt</span>
            <button id="cpy7" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent7()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">touch - create a new empty file or update the timestamp of an existing file</span>
            <span id="myText8" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">touch null.txt</span>
            <button id="cpy8" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent8()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">cat - concatenate and display files</span>
            <span id="myText9" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">cat example.txt</span>
            <button id="cpy9" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent9()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">man - manual for a command</span>
            <span id="myText10" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">man ls</span>
            <button id="cpy10" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent10()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">htop - an interactive process viewer and system monitor</span>
            <span id="myText11" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">htop</span>
            <button id="cpy11" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent11()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">gzip - compress files</span>
            <span id="myText12" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">gzip file.txt</span>
            <button id="cpy12" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent12()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">gunzip - decompress compressed files</span>
            <span id="myText13" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">gunzip file.txt.gz</span>
            <button id="cpy13" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent13()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">ssh - connect to a remote server securely</span>
            <span id="myText14" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">ssh username@server_address</span>
            <button id="cpy14" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent14()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">scp - securely copy files between systems</span>
            <span id="myText15" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">scp myfile.txt user@remotehost:/home/user/</span>
            <button id="cpy15" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent15()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">ping - test network connectivity</span>
            <span id="myText16" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">ping 8.8.8.8</span>
            <button id="cpy16" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent16()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">ifconfig - display or configure network interfaces</span>
            <span id="myText17" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">ifconfig</span>
            <button id="cpy17" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent17()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">netstat - display network connection information</span>
            <span id="myText18" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">netstat</span>
            <button id="cpy18" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent18()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">systemctl - control system services and settings</span>
            <span id="myText19" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;"># Start the nginx service<br/>systemctl start nginx<br/><br/># Check the status of the nginx service<br/>systemctl status nginx<br/><br/># Stop the nginx service<br/>systemctl stop nginx</span>
            <button id="cpy19" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent19()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">route - view or configure network routing tables</span>
            <span id="myText20" class="w-75 text-light py-1 px-3 bg-secondary rounded" style=" overflow: auto; white-space: nowrap;">route [options] [add/delete/show]</span>
            <button id="cpy20" class="text-primary fw-bold btn border-0 d-flex align-items-start" onclick="copyContent20()">Copy !</button>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column py-2">
            <span class=" py-2 fw-bolder">top - display system resource usage and processes </span>
